call the reactionism

01:17:48.000 --> 01:17:52.630
of the current political
crises of the moment.

01:17:52.630 --> 01:17:55.300
- I identify with
reaction, personally.

01:17:55.300 --> 01:17:56.580
But, no.

01:17:56.580 --> 01:17:57.320
But, yes.

01:17:57.320 --> 01:17:57.820
No, no.

