collections in different series

01:38:11.050 --> 01:38:12.970
to attract researchers.

01:38:12.970 --> 01:38:17.780
It's interesting to me that--
What kind of involvement

01:38:17.780 --> 01:38:21.590
did the donor have in
naming the collection?

01:38:21.590 --> 01:38:23.630
- He was actually very involved.

