01:38:42.170 --> 01:38:42.990
- Wow.

01:38:42.990 --> 01:38:44.120
Yeah.

01:38:44.120 --> 01:38:49.430
- I want to say that that
collection at Brown as well

01:38:49.430 --> 01:38:54.720
as University of Kansas,
