even if it wasn't conservative.

01:46:02.620 --> 01:46:06.090
So, from my work, women would
call themselves patriotic.

01:46:06.090 --> 01:46:08.320
That was their word
for conservative

01:46:08.320 --> 01:46:11.860
before conservatism
was a movement.

01:46:11.860 --> 01:46:14.870
And so when we
raise this question

01:46:14.870 --> 01:46:18.930
