and set those terms.

01:46:25.040 --> 01:46:28.960
Do you have any ideas of
what those terms might be?

01:46:28.960 --> 01:46:31.050
- I mean, there are a
lot of different terms.

01:46:31.050 --> 01:46:34.240
I know we're short
