thinking about how

01:46:35.870 --> 01:46:40.910
some of these organizations
that identify as, like you said,

01:46:40.910 --> 01:46:44.530
patriotic or identifying
coalesce around certain issues

01:46:44.530 --> 01:46:47.660
but then argue that they're
nonpartisan or political

01:46:47.660 --> 01:46:50.600
or what have you,
